The lemon juice itself was refreshing and perfectly balanced - not too sour, with just the right amount of sweetness. It was clear that they used fresh ingredients, which made a noticeable difference in the taste.

Overall, my visit to La Perla Nutrition Club was enjoyable, and I would definitely recommend their lemon juice to anyone looking for a refreshing and healthy drink option. The combination of great service and a delicious beverage made for a wonderful experience.; ;

